---
import BaseLayout from '~/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About a → b — a private, browser-based file converter"
  description="a → b is a free file converter built around one promise: your files never leave your browser. Here's why it exists, how it's free, and how it's fast."
>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="eyebrow">About</div>
    <h1>A file tool that keeps to itself.</h1>

    <p>
      a → b started from a small frustration: every “free online converter” wants to upload your
      file to a server you’ve never heard of, wrapped in ads and trackers, to do something your own
      computer could do in a second.
    </p>
    <p>
      So this one doesn’t. Every conversion runs inside your browser using WebAssembly. Your files
      are read into memory, transformed on your own CPU, and handed back — they never touch a
      network. You don’t have to take our word for it: open your browser’s Network tab and watch it
      stay empty while you work.
    </p>
    <p>
      No accounts. No tracking. No file-size games designed to sell you a subscription. Just a
      small, sharp set of tools that respect your privacy by construction.
    </p>

    <div class="support">
      <div class="support-title">If it saved you a minute</div>
      <div class="support-body">
        a → b is free and always will be. It’s built and maintained by one person. If it’s useful, a
        small tip keeps it caffeinated — entirely optional, never nagged.
      </div>
      <a class="support-cta" href="https://ko-fi.com/rosscyking" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        Support on Ko-fi
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .wrap {
    padding: 48px 0 8px;
    max-width: 68ch;
  }
  .eyebrow {
    font-size: 11.5px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  h1 {
    font-size: 34px;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin: 0 0 20px;
    color: var(--ink);
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  p {
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    margin: 0 0 18px;
  }
  .support {
    border: 1px solid var(--hair);
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 22px;
    background: var(--card);
    margin-top: 10px;
  }
  .support-title {
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .support-body {
    font-size: 14.5px;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    line-height: 1.55;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .support-cta {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    background: var(--accent);
    color: #fff;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 11px 18px;
    font-size: 14.5px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  @media (max-width: 720px) {
    h1 {
      font-size: 27px;
    }
  }
</style>
